description:
This is an assortment of divine items that can change the course of battle. As such, they are rather difficult to find in the game.
*The purchase of this product is limited to once per account. Please note that multiple purchases are not possible.

The following items are included:
-Hand of God x3
-Tears of the Phoenix x3
-Elixir x3
-Fruit of the Star Tree x3
--
Total items: 12
name: Assorted Rare Items of the Gods Set
